title: X-Treme X-Men v2 (001 - 013) (2012 - 2013) (Digital) (Empire)
description:
X-Treme X-Men v2 (001 - 013) (2012 - 2013) (Digital) (Empire) 


An ongoing series written by Greg Pak and drawn by Stephen Segovia, Paco Diaz and Andre Araujo starring a ragtag team of X-Men from alternate Earth. In no way associated with Chris Claremont's title of 2001, which carried the same credentials. This is more of a revamped version of Exiles, with Earth 616's Dazzler as the leading protagonist.
